# Windsurf rules — autoagent

This repo uses a portable `.agent/` brain. Load at session start:

- `.agent/AGENTS.md`
- `.agent/memory/personal/PREFERENCES.md`
- `.agent/memory/semantic/LESSONS.md`
- `.agent/skills/_index.md` (skills load on demand)
- `.agent/protocols/permissions.md` (before any tool call)

Directive: see `program.md`.

Key constraints:
- Never edit below the FIXED ADAPTER BOUNDARY in agent.py/agent-claude.py.
- Never change MODEL from gpt-5.
- First run on any branch is always the unmodified baseline.
- Every iteration runs in a fresh-context subagent.
- Apply the overfitting-check skill before committing.
- Both agent.py (OpenAI SDK) and agent-claude.py (Claude SDK) share this brain.
